text: Ádám Tóth (born 8 September 1998) is a Hungarian handball player for Dabas KK and the Hungarian national team. He represented Hungary at the 2020 European Men's Handball Championship.2020 European Men's Handball Championship squad ==References== Category:Hungarian male handball players Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:Sportspeople from Miskolc
